### List all existing status pages
GET https://betteruptime.com/api/v2/status-pages HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{uptimeApiToken}}

### Get a single status page
# @prompt statusPageId
GET https://betteruptime.com/api/v2/status-pages/{{statusPageId}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{uptimeApiToken}}

# Status Page Resources ===============================================

### List existing resources of a status page
# @prompt statusPageId
GET https://uptime.betterstack.com/api/v2/status-pages/{{statusPageId}}/resources HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{uptimeApiToken}}

### Get a single status page resource
# @prompt statusPageId
# @prompt resourceId
GET https://uptime.betterstack.com/api/v2/status-pages/{{statusPageId}}/resources/{{resourceId}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{uptimeApiToken}}